* '''Setting:''' [[Avernus]]

document_data.DDAL09-16 - Honors Unforeseen:
{{main|Honors Unforeseen}}

Part two of ''Doors and Corners'' series.

{{Quote|''Accompanying the Chosen of Ilmater and bearing the newly discovered Ward of Faithfulness, you proceed further into the tomb of the Bloody Hooves. Time is running short. Zariel’s forces hunt for you even now.''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[Deirdre Donlon]]
* '''Editor(s):''' [[Greg Marks]], [[Hannah Rose]], [[Travis Woodall]]
