document_data.DDAL09-17 - In the Hand:
{{main|In the Hand}}

Part three of ''Doors and Corners'' series.

{{Quote|''Your quest to return the Bloody Hooves is nearly at an end. Only the company’s commander remains and then you’ll be ready to ride to the rescue of fallen Elturel!''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[Paige Leitman]], [[Ben Heisler]]
* '''Editor(s):''' [[Greg Marks]], [[Hannah Rose]], [[Travis Woodall]]
