document_data.DDEP09-01 - Infernal Pursuits:
{{main|Infernal Pursuits}}

{{Quote|''A horse race in Baldur’s Gate becomes a hellish battle on infernal war machines in Avernus when the characters get caught between two evil merchants… and must hang on for dear life.''|}}

* '''Designer(s):''' [[James Introcaso]], [[Shawn Merwin]], [[Will Doyle]]
